      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, qualitative justification of turbulence model and hemolysis correlation selection is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published literature consensus for rotating blood pump flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law correlation used per FDA guidance. Qualitative justification documented."
    },
    {
